      },
      "date": "2018-09-18 17:45:39.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nActually their is a trick to create extra compatible fields. Just do the following:\n\n#define max_short_io_bytes_show  short_io_bytes_show\n#define max_short_io_bytes_store  short_io_bytes_store\n\nLUSTRE_RW_ATTR(max_short_io_bytes);\n\nOf course add this to osc_attrs. \n\nIn this case it might be a good idea to swap the names. Make max_short_io_bytes_*** () the default function names.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
